<section xml:id="following">
<title>Follow along…</title>

<para>If you're interested in tracking the development of XML Calabash,
you might be interested in:</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Following the discussion on
<link xlink:href="mailto:xproc-dev-request@w3.org">xproc-dev</link>
(archived at
<link xlink:href="http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/xproc-dev/">lists.w3.org</link>.
XProc-dev is a general XProc discussing list, not limited specifically to
XML Calabash.
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>Following the code development
<link xlink:href="https://github.com/ndw/xmlcalabash1">at github</link>.
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>Following the
<link xlink:href="https://github.com/ndw/xmlcalabash1/issues">issues list</link>
(<link xlink:href="http://code.google.com/p/xmlcalabash/issues/list">old list</link>).
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>You can even follow <literal>xmlcalabash</literal> on
<link xlink:href="https://botsin.space/@xmlcalabash/">the Fediverse</link>,
if you want.</para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
